@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<div class="container mt-4">

    <h2>Overview</h2>
    <p>
        This Mortgage Calculator is an educational web application created as part of a computer science project.
        It allows users to explore mortgage payment estimates and loan eligibility scenarios.
    </p>

    <h2>Information Usage</h2>
    <p>
        The application processes user-provided information such as loan amounts, interest rates, income, and
        other financial inputs solely for the purpose of performing mortgage calculations.
    </p>
    <p>
        This information is used only during your active session and is not associated with any user account.
    </p>

    <h2>Data Storage</h2>
    <p>
        The application does not permanently store personal or financial information.
        Loan input data may be temporarily retained during navigation to support recalculation and adjustment,
        and is cleared when you reset the form or start a new calculation.
    </p>

    <h2>Cookies and Session Data</h2>
    <p>
        Temporary session data may be used to support application functionality.
        No tracking, analytics, or advertising cookies are used.
    </p>

    <h2>Information Sharing</h2>
    <p>
        This application does not share, sell, or transmit user-provided information to third parties.
    </p>

    <h2>Disclaimer</h2>
    <p>
        All results provided by this calculator are estimates only and are not financial advice
        or a loan commitment. Users should consult qualified financial professionals before
        making financial decisions.
    </p>

    <p class="text-muted mt-4">
        <small>Last updated: @DateTime.Now.ToString("MMMM dd, yyyy")</small>
    </p>

</div>